  },
  {
    q: "How important is it to have a website versus selling only on Instagram?",
    a: "Having your own website gives you complete control over the buyer experience, customer data, and brand presentation. Instagram can ban or restrict accounts without warning. A website with SEO can also attract organic buyers who search Google for specific products. We recommend both working together, with Instagram driving discovery and your website handling the purchase."
  },
