  },
  {
    q: "How do we create seasonal campaigns for Navratri or Diwali fashion collections?",
    a: "We plan your festival campaign calendar at least 8 weeks in advance. Navratri collections are promoted from mid-August onwards. Diwali collections launch in September. Wedding season content starts in October. This advance planning ensures your inventory sells before the season, not after. Campaign budgets are concentrated in the 2 to 3 weeks of peak buying."
  },
  {
    q: "How much should we spend on Facebook and Instagram ads for a fashion brand?",
    a: "For a fashion brand starting with performance marketing in India, a monthly Meta Ads budget of ₹15,000 to ₹30,000 is a reasonable starting point for meaningful testing and initial sales generation. During peak festival seasons we recommend increasing this. We provide revenue projections based on your average order value and target sales before any campaign starts."
  }
];
